@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultTextAlignment left
skinparam ArrowColor #1F2937
skinparam rectangle {
  FontColor #111827
  BorderColor #1F2937
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #DCFCE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #15803D

title React Tests After: Preserved Symlink Resolution

rectangle "node --preserve-symlinks\n--import tsx --test" as Runner #D1FAE5
rectangle "react-test-renderer\n(require('react'))" as RTR #BBF7D0
rectangle "SDK/Test imports\n(import 'react')" as SDK #BBF7D0
rectangle "Hooks Runtime" as Runtime #E5E7EB

Runner --> RTR
Runner --> SDK
RTR --> Runtime : React singleton
SDK --> Runtime : Same React singleton

note right of Runtime
Module path canonicalization is stable.
Hooks dispatcher is shared.
React hook tests execute successfully.
end note
@enduml
